{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Build a premium, modern, high-converting Shopify homepage hero section for Titan Express, a Sydney-based Removalist, Man and Van, and Furniture Delivery business.
    
    PRIMARY OBJECTIVE
    
    This section must be designed to:
    
    • Increase Google Ads Quality Score
    • Improve Landing Page Relevance
    • Clearly communicate all services to both users and Google's AI systems
    • Generate phone calls and quote requests
    • Establish trust within the first few seconds
    • Work perfectly on mobile devices where most visitors arrive from Google Ads
    
    BUSINESS SERVICES
    
    Titan Express provides:
    
    • Removalist Sydney
    • Man and Van Sydney
    • Furniture Delivery Sydney
    • Furniture Removalist Sydney
    • Single Item Delivery Sydney
    • Marketplace Pickup & Delivery
    • Store Collection & Delivery
    • Small Apartment Moves
    • Granny Flat Moves
    • Same Day Furniture Delivery
    • Same Day Removalist Service
    • Local Sydney Moving Services
    
    TOP CONTACT BAR
    
    Create a slim sticky top bar above the hero section.
    
    Text:
    Need a Removalist Today?
    
    Primary Button:
    📞 Call 0469 717 535
    
    The phone button must be highly visible on mobile and desktop.
    
    Include subtle pulse animation on the phone button.
    
    HERO HEADLINE (H1)
    
    Same Day Removalist & Man With Van Sydney
    
    SECONDARY TEXT
    
    Furniture Delivery • Small Moves • Marketplace Pickup • Store Collection
    
    SUBHEADING
    
    Titan Express provides affordable furniture delivery, single item transport, apartment moves, granny flat moves, Marketplace pickup and store collection services throughout Sydney.
    
    CALL TO ACTIONS
    
    Primary Button:
    Call Now
    
    Secondary Button:
    Get Free Quote
    
    TRUST BADGES
    
    Display visually appealing badges:
    
    ✓ Same Day Available
    
    ✓ Oversized Van
    
    ✓ Professional Mover
    
    ✓ Furniture Protection
    
    ✓ Trolley & Blankets
    
    ✓ Sydney Wide Service
    
    SERVICE KEYWORD CHIPS
    
    Display interactive service chips:
    
    Removalist Sydney
    
    Man and Van Sydney
    
    Furniture Delivery Sydney
    
    Furniture Removalist Sydney
    
    Small Apartment Moves
    
    Single Item Delivery
    
    Marketplace Pickup
    
    Store Collection Delivery
    
    Same Day Delivery
    
    Granny Flat Moves
    
    DESIGN STYLE
    
    Create a premium service-business appearance.
    
    Use:
    
    • Modern layout
    • White background
    • Black text
    • Yellow / Gold accent colours
    • Small blue trust accents
    • High-end service company feel
    • Professional removalist branding
    • Clean spacing
    • Modern typography
    • No clutter
    • No outdated elements
    
    ADVANCED SVG REQUIREMENTS
    
    Use modern custom SVG graphics:
    
    • Oversized moving van
    • Furniture trolley
    • Moving boxes
    • Sofa icon
    • Route lines
    • Location pins
    • Direction arrows
    • Delivery path graphics
    
    SVG elements should feel premium and interactive.
    
    INTERACTIVE REQUIREMENTS
    
    The section must be highly interactive:
    
    • Hover effects
    • Floating badges
    • Smooth animations
    • Micro interactions
    • Animated route paths
    • Animated service icons
    • Interactive service chips
    • Button animations
    • Modern card effects
    
    Keep all animations smooth and professional.
    
    USER EXPERIENCE REQUIREMENTS
    
    The section must be:
    
    User-Friendly:
    Easy to understand instantly.
    
    Responsive:
    Works perfectly on mobile, tablet and desktop.
    
    Streamlined:
    No unnecessary elements.
    
    Intuitive:
    Naturally guides users to call or request a quote.
    
    Interactive:
    Encourages engagement and action.
    
    Accessible:
    Readable text, proper contrast and touch-friendly buttons.
    
    Functional:
    Every element must serve a purpose.
    
    PERFORMANCE REQUIREMENTS
    
    • Fast loading
    • Lightweight code
    • No external libraries
    • Optimised for mobile devices
    • No layout shift
    • No horizontal scrolling
    • SEO-friendly structure
    • Clean HTML and CSS
    
    GOOGLE ADS LANDING PAGE OPTIMISATION
    
    The hero section should clearly communicate:
    
    Who we are:
    Titan Express
    
    What we do:
    Removalist, Man and Van, Furniture Delivery
    
    Where:
    Sydney NSW
    
    Why choose us:
    Same Day Service, Oversized Van, Professional Handling
    
    What action to take:
    Call Now or Request Quote
    
    SEO REQUIREMENTS
    
    Use a single H1 only.
    
    Naturally include:
    
    Removalist Sydney
    
    Man and Van Sydney
    
    Furniture Delivery Sydney
    
    Furniture Removalist Sydney
    
    Small Moves Sydney
    
    Single Item Delivery Sydney
    
    Marketplace Pickup Sydney
    
    Store Collection Delivery Sydney
    
    Same Day Removalist Sydney
    
    Include a short SEO-rich business description below the hero.
    
    SCHEMA REQUIREMENTS
    
    Include JSON-LD schema for:
    
    Business Name:
    Titan Express
    
    Business Type:
    MovingCompany
    
    Phone:
    0469 717 535
    
    Service Area:
    Sydney NSW
    
    Services:
    Removalist Sydney
    Man and Van Sydney
    Furniture Delivery Sydney
    Small Apartment Moves
    Granny Flat Moves
    Marketplace Pickup
    Store Collection Delivery
    Single Item Delivery
    
    OUTPUT REQUIREMENTS
    
    Provide complete Shopify-compatible code.
    
    Include:
    
    • HTML
    • CSS
    • SVG
    • JavaScript
    
    Use clean class names beginning with:
    
    titan-hero-
    
    The final result should look like a premium removalist company website designed specifically to maximise Google Ads performance, SEO relevance, user engagement, and phone call conversions.
    , ad a Photo Above The Heading  Remove Get Quote Button Change The Call Now Button Make it A service Style 
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .titan-hero-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .titan-hero-top-bar-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.top_bar_bg }};
    padding: 12px 20px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .titan-hero-top-bar-text-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.top_bar_text_color }};
  }

  .titan-hero-phone-btn-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.phone_btn_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.phone_btn_text_color }};
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.3);
  }

  .titan-hero-phone-btn-{{ai_gen_id}}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.phone_btn_hover }};
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.4);
  }

  .titan-hero-phone-icon-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    animation: titan-hero-pulse-{{ai_gen_id}} 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes titan-hero-pulse-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }
  }

  .titan-hero-container-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .titan-hero-content-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .titan-hero-image-wrapper-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    margin: 0 auto 30px;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .titan-hero-image-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  .titan-hero-h1-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.h1_size }}px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: {{ block.settings.h1_color }};
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .titan-hero-secondary-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.secondary_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.secondary_color }};
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .titan-hero-subheading-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subheading_color }};
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 40px 0;
  }

  .titan-hero-cta-group-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .titan-hero-btn-primary-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.primary_btn_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.primary_btn_color }};
    padding: 18px 50px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.4);
    border: none;
  }

  .titan-hero-btn-primary-{{ai_gen_id}}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.primary_btn_hover }};
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.5);
  }

  .titan-hero-btn-icon-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
  }

  .titan-hero-badges-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .titan-hero-badge-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.badge_bg }};
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .titan-hero-badge-{{ai_gen_id}}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  .titan-hero-badge-icon-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .titan-hero-badge-text-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.badge_text_color }};
  }

  .titan-hero-chips-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .titan-hero-chip-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.chip_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.chip_text }};
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.chip_border }};
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .titan-hero-chip-{{ai_gen_id}}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.chip_hover_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.chip_hover_text }};
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .titan-hero-svg-container-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
    opacity: 0.1;
  }

  .titan-hero-van-svg-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    position: absolute;
    right: 5%;
    top: 20%;
    width: 300px;
    height: auto;
  }

  .titan-hero-box-svg-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    position: absolute;
    left: 5%;
    bottom: 20%;
    width: 150px;
    height: auto;
  }

  .titan-hero-seo-text-{{ai_gen_id}} {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 50px auto 0;
    padding: 30px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.seo_bg }};
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: {{ block.settings.seo_text_color }};
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .titan-hero-top-bar-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
    }

    .titan-hero-top-bar-text-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .titan-hero-phone-btn-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .titan-hero-container-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      padding: 40px 16px;
    }

    .titan-hero-image-wrapper-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .titan-hero-h1-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.h1_size | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .titan-hero-secondary-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.secondary_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .titan-hero-subheading-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .titan-hero-cta-group-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .titan-hero-btn-primary-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .titan-hero-badges-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .titan-hero-badge-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      padding: 12px 14px;
    }

    .titan-hero-badge-text-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .titan-hero-chip-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      font-size: 12px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
    }

    .titan-hero-van-svg-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      width: 200px;
    }

    .titan-hero-box-svg-{{ai_gen_id}} {
      width: 100px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<titan-hero-{{ai_gen_id}} class="titan-hero-{{ai_gen_id}}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
